string-array.name: models_about
string-array.item:
•You get double the model’s price directly from the two supportive friends (first generation)
 •You Permanently exit the model after getting double the model’s price from the two friends.
 •You can join again by paying model’s price to the friend who you should pay for.


•The fees amounts are directly sent between friends separately outside the site.
 •The friends are dealing by their national currency, by a fixed measuring unit which is equivalent to dollars
 •The model’s price is determined from 4 choices which are: 25 dollars, 50 dollars, 75 dollars, 100 dollars.
 •By using the model, you agree on the policies, terms and conditions
